Hukumar kula da yanayi ta kasa ta kasa ta sanar da cewa za a yi ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata a yankin yammacin Arizona, ta kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
