A wasu yankunan kudu maso yammacin hamada, ciki har da Stjenjak da Great Pool, akwai yiwuwar ruwan sama daga 25 zuwa 50 mm, tare da yiwuwar yawan adadin da aka keɓe har zuwa 100 mm.
