Trump yana gudanar da taron a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara yakin neman zabe a taron jama'a da dama a Wheeling, West Virginia a yau.
Wannan ne taro na farko daga cikin taro biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da ziyarar gajere zuwa Tennessee da Mississippi.
Trump bai riga ya kada kuri'arsa ba don sabon alƙali na Kotun Koli kuma yana shirin kara goyon baya ga zaben da ke tafe saboda akwai haɗarin cewa 'yan Republican za su rasa rinjayensu a majalisar bayan zaben da aka yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai fara a West Virginia a yau da dare, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne don karfe 7 na yammacin yamma, a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi sharhi a kan sauraron da ake yi a wannan makon na dan takarar kotun koli Bret Kavanaugh wanda ya jawo jayayya a kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu nasara a zaben watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, ofishin shugabancin Trump ya ce taron biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, za su "ƙawata masu son yin aiki da goyon baya" domin 'yan Republican suna ƙoƙarin riƙe da rinjaye a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma Majalisar Dattijai, in ji Reuters.
"Yawancin majalisar dokoki yana da muhimmanci sosai ga shirin shugaban kasa cewa zai yi tafiya zuwa kasashe da dama yayin da muke shiga cikin gwagwarmayar yakin neman zabe", wani mai magana da yawun Trump da ba a san shi ba ya shaidawa Reuters.
Wannan taron da za a yi a Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling a yau zai iya jawo hankalin masu sauraro daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, inda ya lashe gasar a shekarar 2016 da maki sama da 40 bisa dari.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican, Patrick Morrissey daga West Virginia, wanda ya yi koma baya a cikin kuri'u.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya taimaka masa ya inganta darajarsa a cikin binciken", in ji masanin siyasa Simon Haedar na Jami'ar West Virginia ga Reuters.
