Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afku a yammacin yankin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya afku da ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Ƙarfin girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya afku a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
