A shekara ta 2006: Girman digiri 6.8 ya afku a kudancin tsibirin Java, mafi yawan mutane a Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya afku a gabar kudu, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
A shekara ta 2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta jawo lalacewa da firgici domin ta tunasar da mutane game da lalacewar da ta faru a cikin mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon faɗuwar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok, a ƙasar Indonesia, inda mutane fiye da 500 suka mutu, yawanci a arewacin tsibirin.
