An kama ɗansa na farko, Sara Palin, bisa zargin yin zalunci a cikin iyali
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne bisa zargin kai hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, a birnin Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin yin ta'addanci a cikin iyali, hana rahoton yin ta'addanci a cikin iyali, da kuma hana shi yin hakan, in ji wani rahoto da jami'in 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska ya fitar a ranar Asabar.
Wani rahoto na 'yan sanda ya ce, sa'ad da wata 'yar'uwa ta yi ƙoƙari ta kira 'yan sanda don su ba da rahoton laifin da ta yi, sai ya ɗauke ta wayar.
An tsare Palin a tsare da Mat-Su kuma yana riƙe da asusun ajiya na $500, rahoton KTUU.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda a lokacin da ake tambayarsa game da ikirarin laifinsa ya bayyana cewa, "Na'am", in ji cibiyar sadarwa.
Palina yana da laifin aikata laifuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin zai iya yin shekara guda a kurkuku da kuma tarar da dala 250,000.
An kuma zarge shi da laifin aji na B, wanda ke ɗauke da hukuncin ɗaurin kurkuku na kwana ɗaya da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka shigar da karar da ta shafi Palin ba.
A watan Disamban shekarar 2017, an zarge shi da harin da ya kai wa mahaifinsa Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton cewa an kai mata hari.
Wannan shari'ar tana gaban Kotun Tsohon Soji a Alaska.
