Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa mai wuya ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayful Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas.
Saipov (30) ya yi amfani da motar hayar gidan sayar da kayayyaki Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar keke a kan West Side Road a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa 'yan ƙafa da kuma masu hawa keke da suka taru a kan hanyar a watan Oktoba
Don a yi amfani da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su tabbatar da cewa Saibo ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar a kotun kudancin New York.
Duk waɗannan abubuwan sun kai ga hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardar kotu.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta yanke hukuncin kisa a kan Saipov da laifin da ya kai maki 22, wanda ya hada da laifin kisa da kuma saɓo guda takwas da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a harkokin aikata laifuka, da kuma laifin zalunci da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci shiri da kuma tunani sosai, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai shi a matsayin mummunan, mummunan, da kuma lalatacce.
Saifullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandra Damian Pagnucca asarar rai da kuma asarar rai, kamar yadda sanarwar da aka bayar ta ce.
Wadanda aka kashe su biyar 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ta shige tun lokacin da kotun kudancin New York ta yi shari'ar kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa a kan masu sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
An yi kisa ta ƙarshe a cikin shari'ar tarayya a New York a shekara ta 1953, lokacin da aka kashe ma'aurata Julius da Ethel Rosenberg bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe su biyu a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, wanda asalinsa Uzbek ne, ya nuna rashin tuba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
Saiipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, an yi masa wahayi don kai hari, kamar yadda aka ambata a cikin rahoton.
Ya kuma bukaci a cire tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Ya bayyana cewa bai yi laifi ba a kan abubuwa 22 da aka tuhume shi da su.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin masu ba da shawara ga jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saip, ya ce sun yi matukar takaici da hukuncin da masu gabatar da kara suka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin kisa na rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba, zai kara wa duk wadanda suka shiga cikin wannan lamarin da ke damun su".
A baya, ƙungiyar kare hakkin Saipov ta nemi mai gabatar da kara ya hana ta neman hukuncin kisa.
